description: It comes after modelling suggested that infections had reached a plateau thanks to the lockdown.
title: Coronavirus: Number of deaths rises to 530 in Ireland
title_page: Coronavirus: Number of deaths rises to 530 in Ireland - BBC News
maintext: At the start of the crisis, each confirmed case was infecting on average 4.5 people but that figure is now down to between 0.7 and 1 and falling.
